OL,3,CShoplifting on the rise as Welsh
OL,4,Cbusinesses left to foot the bill
OL,6,FWelsh businesses are calling for more
OL,7,Fto be done to tackle shoplifting.
OL,9,FIt comes as UK Government figures
OL,10,Freveal incidents of shoplifting have
OL,11,Fhit a twenty year high.
OL,13,FMore than 440 thousand offences were
OL,14,Frecorded by police in the year to
OL,15,FMarch. Whereas only around 2000
OL,16,Fcautions were accepted for shoplifting
OL,17,Fin the same period, with 431 fines
OL,18,Fhanded out.
