OL,3,CShoplifting on the rise as Welsh
OL,4,Cbusinesses left to foot the bill
OL,6,FThe new Westminster government has
OL,7,Fpromised action to control the rise
OL,8,Fand ensure the crimes do not continue
OL,9,Fto go unpunished.
OL,11,FHowever, in the meantime, Welsh
OL,12,Fbusiness owners say they have had to
OL,13,Ffoot the bill.
OL,15,FSwansea business owner, Julie
OL,16,FRuscitto, showed ITV Wales footage of
OL,17,Fa man entering her shop, the Chocolate
OL,18,FBox, and stealing goods before leaving
OL,19,Fthrough the front door.
