OL,6,FShe recounted: "He just said 'Alright
OL,7,Flove?' and grabbed a display balloon
OL,8,Fwhich has a bottle of prosecco in
OL,9,Fthere and a chocolate hamper... and
OL,10,Fjust walked out the door and closed it
OL,11,Fbehind him. The cameras obviously
OL,12,Fcaught him."
