OL,6,FShe added: "I was in shock to be
OL,7,Fhonest and I couldn't believe it had
OL,8,Fhappened. The rest of the day we were
OL,9,Fcontinuously on edge, for the rest of
OL,10,Fthe week too to be honest, cause you
OL,11,Fdon't know who's going to walk through
OL,12,Fthe door. When somebody just pinches
OL,13,Fsomething, just takes it, it's dipping
OL,14,Fin to the profits all the time."
