OL,3,CShoplifting on the rise as Welsh
OL,4,Cbusinesses left to foot the bill
OL,6,FShoplifting incidents in Wales have
OL,7,Fincreased almost 30% despite
OL,8,Fbusinesses employing more security
OL,9,Fmeasures to counter the increased
OL,10,Frisk. It is a growing problem with
OL,11,Fgrowing repercussions for retailers,
OL,12,Fwho are losing thousands of pounds
OL,13,Fevery year.
OL,15,FSimon Kendrick, who runs the Gamers
OL,16,FEmporium in Swansea, is no stranger to
OL,17,Fshoplifting, and said he experienced
OL,18,Fit on what he described as a
OL,19,Fprofessional level.
