OL,3,CShoplifting on the rise as Welsh
OL,4,Cbusinesses left to foot the bill
OL,6,F"We had a fairly prolific shoplifter
OL,7,Flast year. he came in, he engaged the
OL,8,Fstaff in conversation, he distracted
OL,9,Fthem, he pocketed items. In one
OL,10,Fparticular visit he grabbed around
OL,11,Fseven or eight items while maintaining
OL,12,Fa conversation with the staff and
OL,13,Fmisdirecting their attention so there
OL,14,Fwas definitely an element of
OL,15,Fprofessionalism to him."
