OL,3,CShoplifting on the rise as Welsh
OL,4,Cbusinesses left to foot the bill
OL,6,FHe said: "I think there's a perception
OL,7,Fthat smaller value shoplifting doesn't
OL,8,Faffect businesses. But cumulatively,
OL,9,Fit is a real problem for businesses.
OL,10,FIt's also a real problem for their
OL,11,Fperception of their security.
OL,13,F"We would like to see Police and Crime
OL,14,FCommissioners taking this problem more
OL,15,Fseriously and prioritising it."
